Summary: two star like objects moveing in formation then darting off
divs: Sighting Details i was looking up at the stars in the sky when all of the sudden two stars started moveing both started from the same area one went down in the sky to the edge of the sky at a speed slower than a shooting star and faster and higher up than an airplane.the other one darted around for a minute or so then stopped.this was no airplane or satelite.it moved fast.and lit up at the edge of the sky then dissapeared.
